{"tid":513976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"iPhone6s發脹要求更換被拒　支那男被先達店員打傷","createTime":"2017-12-30T06:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T08:18:07.000Z","uid":5195,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8d61112cfc2b61fdbdbe1672d929a9f5bb34ee2b","tid":513976,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:13:06.000Z","msg":"一名內地男子，早前在亞皆老街先達廣場購買一部iPhone 6手機，使用一直沒問題。約3個月前，他打算買一部iPhone 6s給女兒使用，於是到同一間店舖購買，但該店缺貨，於是到商場另一間店購買，但使用後不久，電池即發脹，更頂爆屏幕。今日上午11時許，他拿着手機到店舖要求更換，但店員不同意，雙方發生爭執，期間內地男被人揮拳打傷右眼，於是報警求助。救護員到場將他送院治理，警方初步調查後，將一名店員拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20171230/photo/bkn-20171230131723152-1230_00822_001_02b.jpg?20171230133925\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20171230%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20171230131723152-1230_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20171230133925&h=0b646217&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6cd47643a18d0945ac4d723f65ccd099d2536878","tid":513976,"uid":25794,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:14:24.000Z","msg":"先達好波"},{"pid":"8948f86b253b22257a9e7de735406fa3e6c2eca1","tid":513976,"uid":85819,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:14:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9f3c4d0b46871062ba95ed3849918e92c8776845","tid":513976,"uid":4455,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:14:52.000Z","msg":"先達狗vs大陸蝗"},{"pid":"4b83b5b95b61f8cded923a26f132164137b826d1","tid":513976,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:16:28.000Z","msg":"香港社會垃圾vs垃圾社會人民"},{"pid":"53f301551599c4a081e45b26ce8515bbef5c4886","tid":513976,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T06:17:10.000Z","msg":"使用不久即係幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n通常二手機都係7日包換，一至三個月店保，過7日幫你整唔包換係正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2afad36356240e67ab03851f44